column5: Enjoy 1723sqft. Beautiful home with nice backyard for your family.Great location within 10-20 minutes from downtown Austin and easy access to HWY 130, 5 min from F1 tract and Austin International Airport. Community pool available and walking distance to nearby Southeast Metro Park, very clean place wide soccer fields, baseball fields and a small playground. It's a terrific place to stay close from special entertainment from downtown and far enough to find some quite and peaceful place to relax.
